			<CASNumber>9002-81-7</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Paraformaldehyde is a common form of formaldehyde for industrial applications. It is a white powder that consists of a polymer of formaldehyde and is used especially as a disinfectant. It is the informal name of polyoxymethylene, a polymer of formaldehyde. It is slowly formed as a white precipitate by condensation from the predominant species methanediol in solutions of formaldehyde. It is used chiefly as an antiseptic.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">多聚甲醛是一种常见的工业用甲醛。它是一种由甲醛聚合物组成的白色粉末，主要用作消毒剂。它是甲醛聚合物聚甲醛的非正式名称。它是由甲醛溶液中的主要物质甲二醇缩合而成的白色沉淀。它主要用作防腐剂。</common:generalComment>
